menu "ESP-Brookesia: Files App Configurations"
    config BROOKESIA_APP_FILES_ENABLE_PRELOAD_DOM
        bool "Preload Files GUI DOM"
        default y
        help
            Preload and retain the Files app GUI DOM when the app is installed.
            This moves JSON UI parse/load cost out of the user-visible launch path
            at the cost of extra resident PSRAM.
endmenu
